                            <comment id="17561129" author="jira-bot" created="Thu, 30 Jun 2022 17:11:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit aad2abc4230c0ad2025ede33e9b2a5186bb5b624 in solr&apos;s branch refs/heads/main from Houston Putman&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://gitbox.apache.org/repos/asf?p=solr.git;h=aad2abc4230&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://gitbox.apache.org/repos/asf?p=solr.git;h=aad2abc4230&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

